title: Ranked Team. Need Players.
body: Hey guys, im thinking about starting a new ranked team because i can just not seem to get out of bronze in solo queue, i am in bronze 5 and i have been trying to get out of bronze for the past 2 years or so but its just not happening, i feel like i can do alot better in a team. add me in the game if you want to join my Ranked team - Get Countered - Deep Sanity -

replies.body: Added you, hopefully you can get dat Silver before end of season.
